          <title>AMD's MI400 APU Set to Revolutionize AI, HPC, and Compute Efficiency in 2026</title>
          <description><![CDATA[AMD's Instinct MI400 APU is set to arrive in 2026, designed for AI, machine learning, and HPC workloads. The new design features two Active Interposer Dies with eight Accelerated Compute Dies, doubling the density of its predecessor.]]></description>
